snippet.title: Maid Cafe on Electric Street - Official INDIE Live Expo Trailer
snippet.description:
Maid Cafe on Electric Street is an RPG simulation dating sim developed by Adventurer's Tavern. Players will manage their own cafe to complete orders, speak with the locals, and perhaps find love on the way. Maid Cafe on Electric Street is launching in Summer 2024 for PC.

#MaidCafeOnElectricStreet #IGN #INDIELiveExpo
